high_descs: Turn around, move to the stove on the left.
Open up the left cabinet above the stove, pick up the left glass in that cabinet.
Turn around, bring the glass to the microwave on the right.
Heat the glass in the microwave.
Bring the heated glass back to the sink on the right.
Put the heated glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated glass in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter and turn left. Walk to the stove and look up at the cabinet.
Take a glass from the cabinet.
Turn around and take a step. Turn to your right and walk to the counter. Raise the glass up to the microwave.
Put the glass inside the microwave and shut the door. After it's done take the glass back out.
Turn around and take a couple steps to turn left to walk towards the sink.
Put the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To take the glass from the microwave to put it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the oven.
Open the cupboard above the oven and remove a glass.
Turn around and walk towards the microwave.
Place the glass in the microwave, use the microwave to warm the glass, and remove the glass from the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed glass in the sink.
